            Our luxury concierge model matches homes with vetted, insured cleaners who meet strict white glove standards.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
            The Valley Clean Team takes care of your home while you focus on what matters. Our professional team ensures a spotless space, tailored to your needs.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center lg:items-start justify-center lg:justify-start space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-6">
            <a href="tel:2568261100" class="flex items-center text-gray-700 hover:text-[#FFA985] transition text-lg">
              <i class="fas fa-phone text-[#FFA985] mr-2 text-xl"></i>
              <span class="font-semibold">256-826-1100</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#066f68606946726e6370676a6a637f656a6367687263676b2865696b" class="flex items-center text-gray-700 hover:text-[#FFA985] transition text-lg">
